              class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-scp font-medium text-zinc-900 bg-yellow hover:bg-yellow/90 transition-colors rounded-lg whitespace-nowrap flex-shrink-0"
            >
              Download resume
            </a>
          </div>
          <Text>
            Want the full picture? Download my resume for a comprehensive look at my experience, key projects, achievements, and technical expertise.
          </Text>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 p-8 md:p-16"></div>
      </header>

